OL,3,CSwansea Bay: Patients removed from
OL,4,Csurgery waiting lists by mistake
OL,6,FA Welsh health board has apologised
OL,7,Fafter three patients were taken off of
OL,8,Fthe orthopaedic surgery waiting lists
OL,9,Fin error.
OL,11,FA report by the Public Service
OL,12,FOmbudsman for Wales has raised
OL,13,Fconcerns about how the whole waiting
OL,14,Flist at has been managed.
OL,16,FThe health board said it has accepted
OL,17,Fthe report's recommendations in full
OL,18,Fand they will be implemented over the
OL,19,Fnext few weeks.
