OL,6,FThe says it expects Swansea Bay to
OL,7,Fimplement the recommendations as soon
OL,8,Fas possible.
OL,10,FPublic Services Ombudsman for Wales
OL,11,Fdoes not oversee health boards as a
OL,12,Fwhole but investigates complaints made
OL,13,Fby members of the public.
OL,15,FOne patient, referred to as Mrs B in
OL,16,Fthe report, was taken off the waiting
OL,17,Flist for her right hip despite only
OL,18,Freceiving treatment on her left.
