OL,6,FThe Public Services Ombudsman for
OL,7,FWales, Michelle Morris, said: "While
OL,8,Fpatients are waiting for surgery on
OL,9,Fthe list, they should be treated
OL,10,Ffairly in relation to the management
OL,11,Fof their place on that list, how they
OL,12,Fare communicated with about the time
OL,13,Fit is likely to take to receive
OL,14,Ftreatment and to have their
OL,15,Fexpectations fairly managed.
