OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "The health board
OL,7,Fhas accepted the Ombudsman's
OL,8,Frecommendations in full and we expect
OL,9,Fthem to implement these as soon as
OL,10,Fpossible."
OL,12,FIn response to the report, said: "We
OL,13,Fsincerely apologise to the three
OL,14,Fpatients whose orthopaedic surgery was
OL,15,Fdelayed because of failings in the way
OL,16,Ftheir appointments were managed.
OL,18,F"We have accepted the Ombudsman's
OL,19,Frecommendations in full and they will
OL,20,Fbe implemented over the next few weeks.
