OL,10,Fthere are no other similar cases, and
OL,11,Fif there are, we will again urgently
OL,12,Fexpedite their care.
OL,14,F"Along with scrutinising our
OL,15,Forthopaedic waiting lists, additional
OL,16,Fstaff training is in place to ensure
OL,17,Freferral to treatment time rules are
OL,18,Ffollowed.
